#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.rename_axis.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.rename\\_axis"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:1 of
msgid "Set the name of the axis for the index or columns."
msgstr "设置索引或列的轴名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:3 of
msgid "Value to set the axis name attribute."
msgstr "用于设置轴名称属性的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:5
#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:15 of
msgid ""
"A scalar, list-like, dict-like or functions transformations to apply to "
"that axis' values. Note that the ``columns`` parameter is not allowed if "
"the object is a Series. This parameter only apply for DataFrame type "
"objects.  Use either ``mapper`` and ``axis`` to specify the axis to "
"target with ``mapper``, or ``index`` and/or ``columns``."
msgstr ""
"应用于该轴值的标量、列表类、字典类或函数变换。注意，如果对象是 Series，则"
"不允许使用 ``columns`` 参数。此参数仅适用于 DataFrame 类型对象。使用 ``"
"mapper`` 和 ``axis`` 来指定要应用 ``mapper`` 的轴，或者使用 ``index`` 和/"
"或 ``columns``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:5
#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:15 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A scalar, list-like, dict-like or functions transformations to apply to "
"that axis' values. Note that the ``columns`` parameter is not allowed if "
"the object is a Series. This parameter only apply for DataFrame type "
"objects."
msgstr ""
"应用于该轴值的标量、列表类、字典类或函数变换。注意，如果对象是 Series，则"
"不允许使用 ``columns`` 参数。此参数仅适用于 DataFrame 类型对象。使用 ``"
"mapper`` 和 ``axis`` 来指定要应用 ``mapper`` 的轴，或者使用 ``index`` 和/"
"或 ``columns``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:11
#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:21 of
msgid ""
"Use either ``mapper`` and ``axis`` to specify the axis to target with "
"``mapper``, or ``index`` and/or ``columns``."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:25 of
msgid "The axis to rename."
msgstr "要重命名的轴。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:27 of
msgid "Also copy underlying data."
msgstr "同时复制底层数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:29 of
msgid ""
"Modifies the object directly, instead of creating a new Series or "
"DataFrame."
msgstr "直接修改对象，而不是创建一个新的 Series 或 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:33 of
msgid "The same type as the caller or None if `inplace` is True."
msgstr "与调用者相同类型的对象，如果 `inplace` 为 True 则返回 None。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:38 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.rename`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:39 of
msgid "Alter Series index labels or name."
msgstr "更改 Series 的索引标签或名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:41 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.rename`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:42 of
msgid "Alter DataFrame index labels or name."
msgstr "更改 DataFrame 的索引标签或名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:44 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Index.rename`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:45 of
msgid "Set new names on index."
msgstr "为索引设置新名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:48 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:49 of
msgid "``DataFrame.rename_axis`` supports two calling conventions"
msgstr "``DataFrame.rename_axis`` 支持两种调用方式"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:51 of
msgid "``(index=index_mapper, columns=columns_mapper, ...)``"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:52 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``(mapper, axis={'index', 'columns'}, ...)``"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:54 of
msgid ""
"The first calling convention will only modify the names of the index "
"and/or the names of the Index object that is the columns. In this case, "
"the parameter ``copy`` is ignored."
msgstr ""
"第一种调用方式只会修改索引名称和/或作为列的 Index 对象的名称。在此情况下"
"，参数 ``copy`` 将被忽略。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:58 of
msgid ""
"The second calling convention will modify the names of the the "
"corresponding index if mapper is a list or a scalar. However, if mapper "
"is dict-like or a function, it will use the deprecated behavior of "
"modifying the axis *labels*."
msgstr ""
"第二种调用方式在 mapper 是列表或标量时，会修改相应索引的名称。但如果 "
"mapper 是字典类或函数，则会使用已被弃用的行为，即修改轴 *标签*。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename_axis.rename_axis:63 of
msgid "We *highly* recommend using keyword arguments to clarify your intent."
msgstr "我们 *强烈* 推荐使用关键字参数来明确你的意图。"

